---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About - Piyush Mehta"
  description="Learn more about Piyush Mehta - Software Engineer, Tech Speaker, and Open Source Enthusiast"
>
  <main>
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <section class="intro">
      <p>
        Hi! I'm Piyush Mehta, a passionate software engineer with expertise in
        building scalable web applications and distributed systems. I love
        sharing knowledge through technical talks, writing, and contributing to
        open source projects.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="experience">
      <h2>What I Do</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>üöÄ Build scalable web applications using modern technologies</li>
        <li>üé§ Speak at conferences and meetups about software engineering</li>
        <li>‚úçÔ∏è Write technical articles and tutorials</li>
        <li>üåü Contribute to open source projects</li>
        <li>üë®‚Äçüè´ Mentor developers and lead technical workshops</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="skills">
      <h2>Technologies I Work With</h2>
      <div class="skills-grid">
        <div class="skill-category">
          <h3>Frontend</h3>
          <p>React, TypeScript, Next.js, Astro, HTML/CSS</p>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-category">
          <h3>Backend</h3>
          <p>Node.js, Python, Microservices, APIs</p>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-category">
          <h3>Cloud & DevOps</h3>
          <p>Azure, AWS, Docker, Kubernetes, CI/CD</p>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-category">
          <h3>Databases</h3>
          <p>PostgreSQL, MongoDB, Redis</p>
