        projects, or speaking at events. Feel free to reach out!
      </p>
      <a href="/contact-me/" class="contact-button">Contact Me</a>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .intro {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #333;
  }

  ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .skills-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .skill-category {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .skill-category h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: #0066cc;
  }

  .contact {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .contact-button {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #0066cc;
    color: white;
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 5px;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .contact-button:hover {
    background: #0052a3;
  }
</style>
